  "title": "Black Pink GUI",
  "description": "A sleek black-and-pink resource pack that modernizes the Minecraft GUI with a stylish, high-contrast look.",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">A full black and pink GUI overhaul that modernizes Minecraft’s menus, UI, title, and fonts with a clean, high-contrast aesthetic.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/21b773f428e538ccc5ed40b888c1b52986b7643e.png\" alt=\"Black Pink GUI title\" width=\"900\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">Supports Mod Menu, Simple Voice Chat, Xaero’s Minimap, and a lot more...</p>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b3045eae50afdff756f668fe7558b71312afd49c.png\" alt=\"Sample\" width=\"200\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7a461e2de62609009280d1a304f9fc728798f5c3.png\" alt=\"Inventory\" width=\"300\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8aceb0b3838e62b89dc3ef4633ad4b493fb161c6.png\" alt=\"Title Screen\" width=\"500\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/db4bfd6057013d9f643e23b142a247d31fe5a6b0.png\" alt=\"Supported Mods\" width=\"450\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">This resource pack specifically supports Simple Voice Chat, Xaero’s Minimap, and Mod Menu, fully covering their custom GUIs.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">Many other mods are also affected automatically, since they use Minecraft’s default UI.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">However, only mods with their own custom interfaces like the ones listed here, require specific support.</p>\n<details>\n<summary>Mod Menu</summary>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bd48e66d31b46e07b747f644766f2a32e8709d2e.png\" alt=\"Mod Menu GUI\" width=\"900\"></p>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Simple Voice Chat</summary>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/12a43521248f4250bf0ad1417aed3d373bbf9387.png\" alt=\"Simple Voice Chat GUI\" width=\"900\"></p>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Xaero’s Minimap</summary>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1d5b3461fc051ee3138c829bc435b3dbb10ea4c2_0.webp\" alt=\"Xaero’s Minimap GUI\" width=\"900\"></p>\n</details>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bea21f7a2df0b717a7bd1a0f4fbc88aaadae63a7.png\" alt=\"Loading Screen\" width=\"450\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/880cb9f543d167a04a7019dda906c05894fd790a.png\" alt=\"Optifine Required\" width=\"300\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">The \"color.properties\" file that changes the Mojang loading screen colors only works when OptiFine is installed, because those color hooks are not part of vanilla Minecraft.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">Without OptiFine, Minecraft simply ignores the loading screen color entries while still loading the rest of the pack.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9fbb8fdb910aa055e5caacdc4e231c5386674b36.png\" alt=\"Mojang Loading Screen\" width=\"750\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">ALL OTHER TEXTURES AND STANDARD RESOURCE PACK FEATURES WORK WITHOUT OPTIFINE AND LOAD NORMALLY.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://optifine.net/downloads\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4c14f141c0a4cf9cdedbd2aebc727f56b5a1914d.png\" alt=\"Optifine Downloads Button\" width=\"500\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/black-pink-gui\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d3cd7c29b765ea051a12413a8580e6b002c04ff.png\" alt=\"Modrinth Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/patrickool/projects\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/425e2c3a8f7ca6ba05b2d4ea767640abc7b5ae71.png\" alt=\"CurseForge Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a></p>",
